    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206683</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">History and Politics Out Loud</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Geschichte und Politik heraus laut</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Histoire et politique dehors fortes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">History e política para fora altos</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Storia e politica fuori forti</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ιστορία και πολιτική έξω δυνατές</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Historia y política hacia fuera ruidosas</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">lets us hear key speeches by Martin Luther King Jr., Winston Churchill, Franklin Roosevelt, Lyndon Johnson, Richard Nixon, and others. Listen to King's I have a dream speech, President Roosevelt's speech to Congress declaring war on Japan, Churchill's iron curtain speech, and more.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">läßt uns Schlüsselreden durch Martin Luther 
König jr., Winston Churchill, Franklin Roosevelt, Lyndon Johnson, 
Richard Nixon und andere hören. Auf I des Königs haben eine 
Traumrede, Präsident Roosevelts Rede zum Kongreß, der Krieg auf 
hören Japan erklärt, Churchills Eisen Vorhangrede und mehr.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">nous laisse entendre les discours principaux par 
le Roi de Martin Luther Jr., Winston Churchill, Franklin Roosevelt, 
Lyndon Johnson, Richard Nixon, et d'autres. Écoutent I du 
Roi ont un discours rêveur, discours du Président Roosevelt's au 
congrès déclarant la guerre la parole de rideau sur du Japon, de 
Churchill fer, et plus.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">deixa-nos ouvir os discursos chaves pelo rei Jr., 
Winston Churchill, Franklin Roosevelt, Lyndon Johnson, Richard Nixon, 
e outro de Martin Luther. Escutam Eu do rei têm um discurso 
ideal, discurso do presidente Roosevelt ao congress que declara a 
guerra o discurso da cortina no ferro de Japão, de Churchill, e mais.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">li lascia sentire i discorsi chiave dal re Jr., 
Winston Churchill, Franklin Roosevelt, Lyndon Johnson, Richard Nixon 
ed altri del Martin Luther. Ascoltano I del re hanno un discorso
di sogno, discorso del presidente Roosevelt al congresso che dichiara 
la guerra con il discorso della tenda di ferro del Churchill, del 
Giappone e più.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">μας αφήνει να ακούσουμε τις βασικές ομιλίες από τη 
νεώτερο Martin Luther King, Winston Churchill, 
Franklin Roosevelt, Lyndon Johnson, Richard Nixon, 
και άλλα. Ακούστε του βασιλιά εγώ έχει μια ομιλία 
ονείρου, την ομιλία Προέδρου Roosevelt's στο συνέδριο 
κηρύσσοντας τον πόλεμο στην Ιαπωνία, την ομιλία κουρτινών 
σιδήρου Churchill, και περισσότερων.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">nos deja oír los discursos dominantes del rey 
Jr., Winston Churchill, Franklin Roosevelt, Lyndon Johnson, Richard 
Nixon, y otros de Martin Luther. Escuchan I de rey tienen un 
discurso ideal, discurso de presidente Roosevelt al congreso que 
declara guerra en el discurso de la cortina del hierro de Japón, de 
Churchill, y más.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
